        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued June 18 at 5:04PM CDT until June 18 at 5:30PM CDT by NWS Topeka KS</headline>
        <description>SVRTOP

The National Weather Service in Topeka has issued a

* Severe Thunderstorm Warning for...
Northern Lyon County in east central Kansas...

* Until 530 PM CDT.

* At 504 PM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located near Bushong,
moving southeast at 25 mph.

HAZARD...Quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Damage to vehicles is expected.

* Locations impacted include...
Americus and Bushong.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
